\begin{enumerate}
    \item[(a)] Find the current flowing in each resistance.
    \item[(b)] Find the power dissipated in each resistance.
    \item[(c)] Compare the total value for the power dissipated in the resistances with the value for the power supplied by the battery.
\end{enumerate}

